                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="quiz"></a>Sanderstead Neighbourhood Care Quiz Night. Sat 4th November</h3>
                <p>Sanderstead Neighbourhood Care’s Quiz Night is on 4th November, 7pm for 7.30pm start. Tickets are £8 in advance or £10 on the door, 6 people per table. Ticket price includes a ploughman's and a dessert, but please bring your own drinks and glasses. Book your tickets by calling 020 8657 8289 or by visiting the SNC office.</p>               
              </td>
